- "seeds of knowledge" metaphorically refers to the number of teachers;
- "blooming rate of academic growth" refers to the average progress score of students;
- "attendance rhythm" metaphorically refers to the average attendance rate;
- "academic season of 2022-2023" specifies the academic year when the progress and attendance were recorded.

